      public Pet​(java.lang.String species, java.lang.String petName, int age, java.lang.String breed, Owner ownedBy)
      Used to construct Pet object.
      Parameters:
      species - must be an animal species
      petName - must be a String, can contain more than one word
      age - must be an integer
      breed - if species is dog or cat, must be a String, else it's null
      ownedBy - must exist, if not program will ask user to create it
